core::cell::Cell::<T>::new.doc:
Creates a new `Cell` containing the given value.

# Examples

```
use std::cell::Cell;

let c = Cell::new(5);
```

core::cell::Cell::<T>::get.doc:
Returns a copy of the contained value.

# Examples

```
use std::cell::Cell;

let c = Cell::new(5);

let five = c.get();
```

